Les organisateurs de la Semaine minière de la RDC font un voyage dans le passé et se tournent vers l'avenir pour amener l'événement à de nouveaux sommets. Over the last 15 years, DRC Mining Week has grown with the mining industry and it has established its footprint in the DRC and the Copperbelt, engaging with the government and key stakeholders. With the success of “face-to-face” interaction with key operators, exploration companies, EPCs and service providers are crucial for improving the quality of mining operations. DRC Mining Week will strive to provide such a platform for networking. REGISTER HERE